# OrganOS Drug Benchmark Big Three
# BACE • BBBP • HIV
#
# Reproducible Molecular Candidate Compression Benchmark
#
# Meaning:
# Total molecules  -> OrganOS active candidates
#
# BACE :  1,513  -> 9
# BBBP :  2,050  -> 9
